        <body>
            
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="san-Latn" rendition="class:nāgarī maturity:undetermined"><!--check script-->
                                                
                <p>
                    <milestone n="A" unit="face" type="pagelike"/><label>First Beam</label>
                    <lb n="1"/>śrī śubhama<unclear>stu</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīmattyā saha gaṁgayā nijagaṇairyuktovimukteśvaro viṁdhyastaṁbhanabhāji kuṁbhatanaye spaṣṭīkṛtānugrahaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kāśīkṣetraniketanādvicalitaḥ prāpto diśaṁ dakṣiṇāṁ sākṣādvrahmaparaṁ nivāsama
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>karodvrāhme sarasyujvale <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <seg rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">1</seg> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tatropāsanayā vicitratarayā te<unclear>na</unclear>rṣiṇā harṣitastasya prārthanayā yatīṁdrapadavīmāsthāya bhūsthāṁ janān <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> mūrttyā sphūrttijuṣā dayārasamayairnetrāṁcalairaṁcitairvākyairjīvaparaikyabodhanaparairvyarthānkṛ 
                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>tārthānvyadhāt· <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <seg rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">2</seg> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Etasyādbhutaceṣṭitasya yaminastasyāvimuktaprabhordhatte pādanamaskriyā tanubhṛtāṁ prājyādhi rājyaśriyaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> saṁdhatte guṇavarṇanāparimaḷaṁ vākye sudhāmādhurīṁ cādhatte smaraṇaṁ pumartthajananīmantaḥparāṁ saṁvidaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
                    <lb n="4"/><seg rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">3</seg> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tenāgastyamunīśvareṇa tapasā prāśastyabhājā punaḥ stotraiścitrapadairupāsya sa śivo nā<unclear>nā</unclear>rtthadaḥ prārtthitaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> khyāte brahmasarastaṭe ghanagirau śrīhemakūṭācale sthāneṣu triṣu ca sthitiṁ ciramagānmaṁgalyaliṁgātmanā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tā
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>pānāṁ tritayaṁ trayaṁ ca vapuṣāṁ nṛṛṇāmavasthātrayaṁ dausthyaṁ netumivācireṇa bhagavānmanyevimuktaśveraḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tristhānīpratirūpamāśrayadiha sthānatrayaṁ vaibhavaiḥ kāṁtaṁ <unclear>kīrji</unclear>tadāyakairaviraḷaiḥ sarvārttinirvāsanaiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <seg rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">5</seg> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bhaktābhīpsita
                
                <milestone n="B" unit="face" type="pagelike"/><label>Second Beam</label>
                
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/>dānanirjaratarorasyāvimukteśituḥ preyān kuṁbhabhavovatīrya sa bhuvi śrīvāmanedrātmanā <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> ratnasvarṇamayairnavopakaraṇai rājopacārocitairdhyānaiścāgamacoditairapacitīraṁtarvahiścācaran· <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <seg rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined"><unclear>6</unclear></seg> <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> giryakṣyagnisudhāmarīciga
                    <lb n="7" break="no"/>ṇite śāke śubhe pārthive varṣe phālgunanāmni māsi dhavaḷe pakṣe daśamyāṁ tithau <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vāre bhānumato grahairanuguṇairaṁgīkṛta maṁga<unclear>laṁ</unclear> bhaktyā bhavyamacīkara<unclear>ddha</unclear>nagirāvetacchilāmaṁdiraṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <seg rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">7</seg> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Etena prathi
                    <lb n="8" break="no"/>tena kuṁbhajanuṣo līlāvatārātmanā <unclear>śrī</unclear>madvāmanayoginā viracitaṁ śaivaṁ śilāmaṁdiraṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ākalpaṁ bhuvi kalpatāṁ ghanaraṇaddhaṇṭāmṛdaṁgāvalībherīḍiṁḍimaśaṁkhakāhalamahāmaṁgalyanādānvitaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>
                    <lb n="9"/><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <seg rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">8</seg> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> dusthatvamasya jagato nikhilasya haṁtuṁ susthatvamāracayituṁ kalitaṁ prayatnāt· <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śaivaṁ śilālayamimaṁ paripālayaṁtu lokadvayīguṇaparāḥ sujanā vidhijñāḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <seg rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">9</seg> <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vidhattāṁmavimukteśo dharmyasyaitasya karmaṇaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> ka
                    <lb n="10" break="no"/><unclear>rtuḥ</unclear> kārayituścānumaṁtuḥ pālayituḥ sukhaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 10 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> maṁgala mahāśrī śrī śrī
                </p>
                
